These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: tomato, spinach
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating spinach and the person who's sport is soccer have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | spinach | tomato  |
| Sport   | soccer    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: peach, papaya
1. the person drinking water and the person eating peach have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | lemonade      | water       |
| Food       | papaya | peach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, classical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, handball
1. the fan electronic and the person who's sport is basketball have different parity positions##9
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | electronic       |
| Sport         | basketball | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: american, russian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
2. the russian and the person who's sport is volleyball have different parity positions##9
3. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | russian | american |
| Sport         | baseball | volleyball  |

 #################################

 
